WEBVTT

00:00:28.427 --> 00:00:31.278
i nalazi se u različitim hranama i pićima.

00:00:31.278 --> 00:00:34.212
Samo provjerite etikete 
slatkih proizvoda koje kupujete.

00:00:34.212 --> 00:00:34.913
Glukoza,

00:00:34.913 --> 00:00:35.695
fruktoza,

00:00:35.695 --> 00:00:36.627
saharoza,

00:00:36.627 --> 00:00:37.495
maltoza,

00:00:37.495 --> 00:00:38.265
laktoza,

00:00:38.265 --> 00:00:38.969
dekstroza,

00:00:38.979 --> 00:00:39.681
i škrob

00:00:39.681 --> 00:00:41.445
su sve vrste šećera.

00:00:41.445 --> 00:00:43.525
Također i kukuruzni sirup s puno fruktoze,

00:00:43.525 --> 00:00:44.309
voćni sok,

00:00:44.309 --> 00:00:45.294
sirovi šećer,

00:00:45.294 --> 00:00:46.521
i med.

00:00:46.521 --> 00:00:49.073
I šećer nije samo 
u slatkišima i desertima,

00:00:49.073 --> 00:00:51.138
dodaje se u umak od rajčice,

00:00:51.138 --> 00:00:51.846
jogurt,

00:00:51.846 --> 00:00:52.777
sušeno voće,

00:00:52.777 --> 00:00:53.856
vodu s okusom,

00:00:53.856 --> 00:00:55.510
ili energetske pločice.

00:00:55.510 --> 00:00:56.603
Pošto je šećer posvuda,

00:00:56.603 --> 00:00:58.026
važno je razumijeti

00:00:58.026 --> 00:00:59.706
kako utječe na mozak.

00:00:59.906 --> 00:01:02.225
Što se događa kad šećer dotakne jezik?